ProduceOrdersController - Class in producereportscontrollers
This class is a Produce Orders Report Controller for ProduceOrdersPage.fxml the function of this class is to display information generated by the system of that information are two tables that show information about the orders, the amount of sales done for each product and profit gained on them, in addition to showing another table that displays each product with the category it is assigned to after reviewing the system-generated reports, the area manager is required to insert information to produce their own report for it to be submitted to the management to see This class also uses other classes to help manage the properties one of the classes is TableRow - which helps us add rows to our table of information with products sold in orders
